title: KrisanatA
text:
Hello! My name is Krisanat Anukarnsakulchularp, or you can call me Otto. My sister drew my profile picture inspired by my favorite animal.
I’m currently working as a Teaching associate at Monash University for the Econometrics and Business Statistics department. My interests are in data structure and visualization.

title: Software
text:
“animbook” is a package to help the user visualize the changes in performance measures and demographic affiliations using animation. It is a package to help prepare, plot, and animate the data.
It is available on CRAN and GitHub
